    dc:creator "Kluge, Nikita" ;
    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "Reclassification of Teloganodes Eaton 1882 (including subgenera Dudgeodes Sartori 2008 and Derlethina Sartori 2008) with a new species from Sulawesi (Ephemeroptera, Teloganodidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7673039>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7673061>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7673077>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7673057>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7673083>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7673063>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7673049> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7673039>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Tergalii figured by Kluge (2004: figs 96E–H) and two classifications of Teloganodes. E, tergalii of T. (Teloganodes) kodai; F, tergalii of T. (Dudgeodes) romani (= Teloganodes/fg1 sp. T4: Kluge 2004); G, tergalii of T. (Dudgeodes) jacobusi (= Teloganodes/fg1 sp. T2: Kluge 2004); H, tergalii of T. (Derlethina) eloisae (= Teloganodes/fg1 sp. T3: Kluge 2004)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7673039/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7673061>
    dc:description "FIGURES 50–60. Tergalii. 50–53, Teloganodes (Dudgeodes) celebensis, tergalii II–V; 54–57, Teloganodes (Dudgeodes) rasus sp. n., tergalii II–V; 58–60, tergalius V of two individuals (59–60, holotype)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7673061/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7673077>
    dc:description "FIGURES 93–94. Teloganodes (Dudgeodes) rasus sp. n., wings of male imago (holotype). 93, in falling light; 94, in transmitted light (arrow shows constant crossvein cua-cup)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7673077/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7673057>
    dc:description "FIGURES 40–45. Teloganodes (Dudgeodes) celebensis. 40–41, penis of male imago, dorsal view; 42, genitalia, ventral view; 43, cuticle of abdominal sternum IX and protopenis of male larva; 44, developing subimaginal penis extracted from the same larva; 45, position of developing penis in larval cuticle of protopenis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7673057/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7673083>
    dc:description "FIGURES 95–101. Teloganodes (Dudgeodes) rasus sp. n., male (holotype). 95–96, penis, dorsal view; 97, genitalia, ventral view; 98–99, halves of subimaginal exuviae of mesonotum, in Canadian balsam and in dry condition; 100–101, hind wing, in falling and transmitted light." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7673083/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7673063>
    dc:description "FIGURES 61–62. Teloganodes (Dudgeodes) rasus sp. n. 61, male larva of last instar; 62, younger female larva." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7673063/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7673049>
    dc:description "FIGURES 19–26. Teloganodes (Dudgeodes) celebensis, exuviae of larval legs. 19–20, fore leg and its fragment; 21, middle leg; 22–26, hind leg and its fragments." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7673049/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

